<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 27 Nov 2023 22:04:29 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>10 月 7 日大屠杀发生前几个月，以色列情报部门收到了令人不寒而栗的警告</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-27/ty-article/.premium/chilling-warnings-picked-up-by-israeli-intelligence-months-before-october-7-massacre/0000018c-1261-dd2e-a5ae-d36ba6240000</link><description>以色列军事情报局的一名士官在 10 月 7 日之前的几个月里发出了 3 次警告，称哈马斯正准备袭击加沙边境附近的以色列社区，但她的话被置若罔闻</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 Nov 2023 20:52:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-27/ty-article/.premium/chilling-warnings-picked-up-by-israeli-intelligence-months-before-october-7-massacre/0000018c-1261-dd2e-a5ae-d36ba6240000</guid></item><item><title>以色列与哈马斯停火、人质换囚犯协议再延长两天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-27/ty-article/.premium/israel-hamas-cease-fire-hostage-for-prisoner-deal-extended-for-two-more-days/0000018c-120c-d2ae-afcf-37de94510000</link><description>哈马斯和以色列均证实有报道称，他们已同意将停火协议延长到周一的最后期限之后，“条件与原始协议相同”。美国希望推动进一步暂停战斗天数</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 Nov 2023 19:45:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-27/ty-article/.premium/israel-hamas-cease-fire-hostage-for-prisoner-deal-extended-for-two-more-days/0000018c-120c-d2ae-afcf-37de94510000</guid></item><item><title>在加沙地带与哈马斯的战争中，以色列抗焦虑药物的使用激增</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-27/ty-article/.premium/use-of-anti-anxiety-medicine-soars-in-israel-amid-war-with-hamas-in-gaza-strip/0000018c-11b7-d2ae-afcf-35f7785e0000</link><description>Clalit HMO 表示，与前一个月相比，10 月份镇静剂和精神科药物的处方数量猛增了 11%。 Maccabi HMO 报告上涨了 20%。 “大多数人都会与专业人士交谈，但如果有人无法正常工作，我们会给他们药物。”</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 Nov 2023 19:10:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-27/ty-article/.premium/use-of-anti-anxiety-medicine-soars-in-israel-amid-war-with-hamas-in-gaza-strip/0000018c-11b7-d2ae-afcf-35f7785e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列对埃隆·马斯克的令人厌恶的拥抱是对犹太人（无论是死的还是活的）的愤世嫉俗的背叛</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-11-27/ty-article/.highlight/israels-repulsive-embrace-of-elon-musk-is-a-cynical-betrayal-of-jews-dead-and-alive/0000018c-11d4-d65f-a7dd-f1d707c80000</link><description>张开双臂欢迎这样一位有毒的大亨，并带他参观在他任内遭到贬低、贬低和否认的大屠杀地点，这应该是内塔尼亚胡遗产上的一个污点</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 Nov 2023 18:14:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-11-27/ty-article/.highlight/israels-repulsive-embrace-of-elon-musk-is-a-cynical-betrayal-of-jews-dead-and-alive/0000018c-11d4-d65f-a7dd-f1d707c80000</guid></item><item><title>佛蒙特州伯灵顿男子因涉嫌仇恨犯罪枪杀三名巴勒斯坦学生而被捕</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-27/ty-article/.premium/man-arrested-for-shooting-three-palestinian-students-in-u-s-in-suspected-hate-crime/0000018c-117f-dd03-a7ff-bf7fd9da0000</link><description>枪击事件发生之际，穆斯林和阿拉伯裔美国人的权利和倡导团体报告称，针对阿拉伯人和穆斯林美国人的仇恨犯罪史无前例地激增</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 Nov 2023 16:29:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-27/ty-article/.premium/man-arrested-for-shooting-three-palestinian-students-in-u-s-in-suspected-hate-crime/0000018c-117f-dd03-a7ff-bf7fd9da0000</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯裔以色列人质逃离哈马斯囚禁，在当地人抓住他之前躲在加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-27/ty-article/russian-israeli-hostage-escaped-hamas-captivity-hid-in-gaza-before-locals-caught-him/0000018c-1121-dd2e-a5ae-d36bfcc40000</link><description>罗尼·克里沃伊 (Roni Krivoi) 是俄罗斯裔以色列人，也是迄今为止唯一获释的成年男性人质，他成功逃离哈马斯几天，但最终在周日被抓获并释放回以色列</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 Nov 2023 16:21:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-27/ty-article/russian-israeli-hostage-escaped-hamas-captivity-hid-in-gaza-before-locals-caught-him/0000018c-1121-dd2e-a5ae-d36bfcc40000</guid></item><item><title>以色列著名人​​权组织敦促国际刑事法院对哈马斯的强奸和其他性犯罪行为进行调查</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-27/ty-article/.premium/prominent-israeli-rights-group-urges-icc-probe-of-hamas-for-rape-and-other-sex-crimes/0000018c-1168-dd03-a7ff-bf78860e0000</link><description>这份由以色列人权医生组织发表的论文提供了哈马斯 10 月 7 日涉嫌性犯罪和基于性别的犯罪的详细清单，这些犯罪已被记录并公开分享。根据已知的情况，该文件得出的结论是，此类暴行“广泛存在”</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 Nov 2023 16:00:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-27/ty-article/.premium/prominent-israeli-rights-group-urges-icc-probe-of-hamas-for-rape-and-other-sex-crimes/0000018c-1168-dd03-a7ff-bf78860e0000</guid></item><item><title>获释的以色列人质让我们得以一睹加沙哈马斯俘虏的生活</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-27/ty-article/.premium/freed-israeli-hostages-offer-glimpse-of-life-in-gaza-as-hamas-captives/0000018c-10fc-d679-abdc-96fcf16d0000</link><description>与 40 名获释人质的家人的对话提供了他们在加沙经历的第一批细节。大多数人被关在隧道里，而其他人则被关在房屋和建筑物中，并担心遭到炮击。有人听到了一项特别的公告来纪念他的九岁生日</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 Nov 2023 15:46:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-27/ty-article/.premium/freed-israeli-hostages-offer-glimpse-of-life-in-gaza-as-hamas-captives/0000018c-10fc-d679-abdc-96fcf16d0000</guid></item><item><title>被哈马斯扣为人质的以色列儿童从加沙获释后开始分享他们的经历</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-27/ty-article/.premium/freed-from-gaza-israeli-children-held-hostage-by-hamas-begin-to-share-their-experiences/0000018c-10e1-d679-abdc-96f9d9590000</link><description>一些人质返回失去亲人的家庭、无家可归的家庭和支离破碎的社区，同时继续为仍被哈马斯扣押的亲人的安全感到焦虑</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 Nov 2023 15:05:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-27/ty-article/.premium/freed-from-gaza-israeli-children-held-hostage-by-hamas-begin-to-share-their-experiences/0000018c-10e1-d679-abdc-96f9d9590000</guid></item><item><title>“战争永远是地狱”：道德哲学家谈以色列在加沙行动的伦理</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-27/ty-article/.premium/war-is-always-hell-moral-philosophers-on-the-ethics-of-israels-battle-with-hamas/0000018c-10b8-d2ae-afcf-35fabe230000</link><description>上个月，牛津大学的40多名学者谴责了以色列国防军在加沙的行动，引发了六位以色列道德哲学家的反驳。在那次交流之后，专家们讨论了战争中什么是“相称的”</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 Nov 2023 14:06:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-27/ty-article/.premium/war-is-always-hell-moral-philosophers-on-the-ethics-of-israels-battle-with-hamas/0000018c-10b8-d2ae-afcf-35fabe230000</guid></item><item><title>德国媒体强调柏林“积极”参与释放哈马斯人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2023-11-27/ty-article/.premium/german-media-emphasizes-berlins-intensive-involvement-in-the-release-of-hamas-hostages/0000018c-107c-d65f-a7dd-f0ffa5370000</link><description>据《南德意志报》报道，德国向以色列派遣了“军事和情报部门”，帮助寻找具有德国公民身份的人质，德国外交官“与卡塔尔保持着持续联系”。前总理亚伊尔·拉皮德告诉《犹太汇报》：“这也是你们的战争”</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 Nov 2023 12:46:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2023-11-27/ty-article/.premium/german-media-emphasizes-berlins-intensive-involvement-in-the-release-of-hamas-hostages/0000018c-107c-d65f-a7dd-f0ffa5370000</guid></item><item><title>以色列与哈马斯的人质交易帮助卡塔尔在10月7日之后改善其形象</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/news/middle-east/2023-11-27/ty-article/.premium/the-hostage-deal-is-helping-qatar-rehabilitate-its-image-after-the-blow-of-october-7/0000018c-1043-d679-abdc-967bffa90000</link><description>10 月 7 日大屠杀之后，由于该国与哈马斯的关系，卡塔尔的形象受到打击。现在，它在导致以色列人质获释的协议中所发挥的作用正在赢得美国和以色列的赞扬</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 Nov 2023 12:42:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/news/middle-east/2023-11-27/ty-article/.premium/the-hostage-deal-is-helping-qatar-rehabilitate-its-image-after-the-blow-of-october-7/0000018c-1043-d679-abdc-967bffa90000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡关于哈马斯的错误前提在开罗找到了合作伙伴</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-27/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-false-premise-about-hamas-had-a-partner-in-cairo/0000018c-101c-dd2e-a5ae-d35f0b4b0000</link><description>塞西将自己定位为以色列和哈马斯之间的唯一调解人，并与内塔尼亚胡一起营造了错误的“金钱会带来和平”的前提。现在，他们必须为后哈马斯加沙的“后天”制定计划</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 Nov 2023 11:20:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-27/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-false-premise-about-hamas-had-a-partner-in-cairo/0000018c-101c-dd2e-a5ae-d35f0b4b0000</guid></item><item><title>操纵大师班：揭露马克斯·布卢门撒尔关于以色列和 10 月 7 日的谎言</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-27/ty-article-opinion/exposing-max-blumenthals-deceptive-claim-israel-is-responsible-for-most-october-7-victims/0000018c-102f-d65f-a7dd-f0ff7b550000</link><description>灰色地带的编辑有否认战争罪的历史，所以毫不奇怪他提供了一篇非常有选择性地使用事实的文章，包括故意编辑的引文以改变其含义，并严重淡化针对以色列人的暴行</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 Nov 2023 10:43:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-27/ty-article-opinion/exposing-max-blumenthals-deceptive-claim-israel-is-responsible-for-most-october-7-victims/0000018c-102f-d65f-a7dd-f0ff7b550000</guid></item><item><title>埃隆·马斯克在加沙停火期间访问以色列，会见内塔尼亚胡和赫尔佐格</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-27/ty-article/.premium/elon-musk-visits-israel-amid-gaza-cease-fire-will-meet-with-netanyahu/0000018c-0fec-d65f-a7dd-ffffd6fe0000</link><description>X 所有者与内塔尼亚胡总理一起参观了 10 月 7 日哈马斯袭击期间摧毁的基布兹之一，然后会见了加沙哈马斯扣押的人质家属</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 Nov 2023 09:35:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-27/ty-article/.premium/elon-musk-visits-israel-amid-gaza-cease-fire-will-meet-with-netanyahu/0000018c-0fec-d65f-a7dd-ffffd6fe0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列司法部考虑如何起诉哈马斯恐怖分子以及可能使用死刑</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-27/ty-article/.premium/israels-justice-ministry-mulls-how-to-prosecute-hamas-terrorists-in-court/0000018c-0c00-d679-abdc-9e387c500000</link><description>由于哈马斯 10 月 7 日大屠杀的性质和规模，以色列司法部面临重大挑战。选择包括集体起诉、军事法庭审判和种族灭绝起诉</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 Nov 2023 09:34:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-27/ty-article/.premium/israels-justice-ministry-mulls-how-to-prosecute-hamas-terrorists-in-court/0000018c-0c00-d679-abdc-9e387c500000</guid></item><item><title>停战期间，加沙人收集尸体、揭露破坏、寻找亲人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-11-27/ty-article-magazine/.premium/during-truce-gazans-gather-bodies-reveal-destruction-seek-relatives/0000018c-0fe5-d65f-a7dd-fff742d10000</link><description>经过七周的轰炸后，停火使加沙人民能够近距离检查他们家园的废墟，或者至少尝试接近他们</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 Nov 2023 09:14:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-11-27/ty-article-magazine/.premium/during-truce-gazans-gather-bodies-reveal-destruction-seek-relatives/0000018c-0fe5-d65f-a7dd-fff742d10000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军称，从哈马斯囚禁中释放的 11 名人质已抵达以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-27/ty-article-live/hamas-seeks-longer-cease-fire-as-sides-enter-final-day-of-swap-39-israelis-freed-so-far/0000018c-0ef1-d679-abdc-9ef9589f0000</link><description>11 名以色列妇女和儿童被哈马斯扣押 52 天后从加沙获释 ■ 以色列和哈马斯同意将停火期限再延长两天 ■ 84 岁以色列人质获释后入院治疗，生命垂危 ■ 至少 1,200 人自 10 月 7 日以来，以色列境内有平民和士兵被杀；加沙仍有 200 多名人质被扣押 ■ 哈马斯控制的卫生部：加沙有 14,854 人死亡</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 Nov 2023 04:46:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-27/ty-article-live/hamas-seeks-longer-cease-fire-as-sides-enter-final-day-of-swap-39-israelis-freed-so-far/0000018c-0ef1-d679-abdc-9ef9589f0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯停火结束后，以色列军队计划扩大加沙攻势</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-27/ty-article/.premium/israels-army-plans-to-resume-offense-on-hamas-in-gaza-once-cease-fire-ends/0000018c-0d1b-d65f-a7dd-fddfd93a0000</link><description>以色列军队决定将行动范围扩大到加沙南部，那里的哈马斯状况要好得多。以色列希望停火让哈马斯有机会看到北部地带的破坏，这可能会削弱继续战斗的动力</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 Nov 2023 04:27:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-27/ty-article/.premium/israels-army-plans-to-resume-offense-on-hamas-in-gaza-once-cease-fire-ends/0000018c-0d1b-d65f-a7dd-fddfd93a0000</guid></item><item><title>在相互压力下，以色列向哈马斯发出信号，如果更多人质获释，则不急于恢复加沙战斗</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-27/ty-article/.premium/israel-signals-to-hamas-no-rush-to-resume-gaza-fighting-if-more-hostages-freed/0000018c-0d75-ddff-a3bc-bdf5e82f0000</link><description>哈马斯对延长停火协议非常感兴趣，该组织告诉卡塔尔人，它将尝试寻找更多符合协议首要标准的以色列人，其中包括约 90 人。以色列国防军也需要时间来更新其部队并为下一阶段做好准备</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 Nov 2023 04:27:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-27/ty-article/.premium/israel-signals-to-hamas-no-rush-to-resume-gaza-fighting-if-more-hostages-freed/0000018c-0d75-ddff-a3bc-bdf5e82f0000</guid></item></channel></rss>